verbose_text: In addition, high expression of CD44 associated with the CSCs characteristic (sphere and colony formation assay, CSCs marker expression and CSC related transcription factor Oct-4 expression level, tumorigenic ability in vivo, SP cells) was testified through the comparison of the CD44 based sorted B16F10-CD44 + (92.3%) and B16F10-CD44 - (29.4%) cells.
